{"tid":41933,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[SoSad音樂]你最近辭職嗎 為了坐上那特首嗎《品客走埋》MV","createTime":"2016-12-16T09:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T08:13:58.000Z","uid":50360,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ecc73ee4f89461e073749b2aa3f20942781d56","tid":41933,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"上星期五，689 宣佈不尋求連任。今個星期一，品客叔叔曾俊華宣佈辭去財政司司長一職。特首跑馬仔已經開始，之後相信仲有葡萄葉劉同主張延續689 政策嘅林鄭宣佈參選。BTW，特首雖然係香港之首，作為香港人，應該有份投票，但到依家都係得個睇字。喂，幾時唔駛靠1200人小圈子選舉，我可以投票先？<br />\n<br />\n品客叔叔職已辭，下一步相信係宣佈角逐特首之位。<br />\n<br />\n《品客走埋》MV：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n9NBIGq05CQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn9NBIGq05CQ&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e449daa7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n9NBIGq05CQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dj57iqcl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdj57iqcl&h=48b23e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1122346f84fb22c321568c2a464832833d7a817e","tid":41933,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"《品客走埋》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：耿耿於懷<br />\n改編填詞：山卡啦<br />\n主唱：挽歌之聲<br />\nMV製作：山卡啦<br />\n<br />\n你  最近辭職嗎  為了坐上那特首嗎<br />\n最近  又頻密露面  已冇驚怕是嗎<br />\n<br />\n當初你我聽聽振英講得好誇<br />\n我想聽你意見  你卻又沒話<br />\n日前誰亮劍  689被棄  等落馬<br />\n這些機會你明嗎<br />\n<br />\n*難道做事極懶惰  當掃把星的庸才<br />\n試圖與你競賽  你覆得多自在<br />\n司長跟葡萄儀比賽<br />\n然後你再串佢  串佢過去放不開<br />\n <br />\n林鄭日夜在靠害  不答惹公關成災<br />\n是誰再放暗箭  誰望著特首位難耐<br />\n看見各個衝上台  把握時間  發動這比賽*<br />\n<br />\n你  最近才休假  部署與那葡萄開打<br />\n最後  是林鄭入閘  那老太發怒嗎<br />\n<br />\n一班建制派裡你功績都不差<br />\n可惜西化爾雅  這算是罪吧<br />\n若然民望夠  就算支持你  不造馬<br />\n入閘後中央照打<br />\n<br />\nRepeat*<br />\n<br />\n難道做事極懶惰  當掃把星的庸才<br />\n試圖與你競賽  有種酸好實在<br />\n揀香港龍頭誰選過<br />\n從沒有  這票尾  我要抱怨太不該<br />\n<br />\n誰為入閘沒按捺  得到賜福不離開<br />\n往後到了決賽  無奈是大家罰站場外<br />\n政制變化總會來  我想投票  決定這比賽"},{"pid":"69be0df69a6a9223474ffd1e0c6fb4b0f9f6a532","tid":41933,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf0d41cca1111b3a00e0a411e60e87e1d8708ae","tid":41933,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f783d47d83e4f3ab1311b51a8a7e6d02dd2d0e","tid":41933,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb1c548ccf16df80b826ae10ef0823048ab2cdb","tid":41933,"uid":49767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02093da43bfff6cefdf2c70b2d8021bc7579d1a","tid":41933,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1551750fd067a21c5651d9f344e4eb84d551c2e6","tid":41933,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15190e27ce79a2d12b171fff2353b129e60482b","tid":41933,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n挽巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73f462ffa9f5855c88449cff7897c9653448c79","tid":41933,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.